{"tid":1552748,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"生於亂世，連登係有種責任","createTime":"2019-09-08T11:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T12:31:27.000Z","uid":318070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b2222368e3c72790c7b01f9ed02d5294a473b6af","tid":1552748,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"正如題目所講，生於亂世，連登是有種責任。<br />\n大家都知道，大家關注的事，討論的事，很快就沉於大海，想重拾，也不知從何找起。每天的資訊都很多，導致很快被大家遺忘。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我懇求連登admin，在時事區，能夠長期置頂大家關注的事。<span style=\"color: red;\">方便大家找尋之餘，也能夠避免高質量的post沉於海底。只需要設置一個置頂區，再分門別類。</span>推到讓admin看到。<br />\n有討論價值的話，大家可以高談闊論。<br />\n沒有的話，就讓它下沉吧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讓成果不斷積累，讓我們不斷進步<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps:內容用書面語表達，標題口語化。因為本身現在在大陸工作，若口語表達的話，實諸多出錯。望大家諒解。<br />\n第二次正式出post,希望大家手下留情，屌少點"},{"pid":"851ab65ae65d487dbf2551a20f9339022ddaf234","tid":1552748,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:51:11.000Z","msg":"好驚被ban ac<br />\n不過都要自推"},{"pid":"b7ff8cbd441c9c6b42b25af93b5e7c041b7e843e","tid":1552748,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4fa7e13c08a98cb46309dabe4da111e03264b53f","tid":1552748,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:51:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a93d640aaa632635212cf7cde0cb22b6ef176285","tid":1552748,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:51:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4741c6b620e10310b02416b22a56ba8a4ba4aba9","tid":1552748,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:52:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"31b19d3ad2af0d286f120944bff349ea0d723963","tid":1552748,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:52:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e93516a3cb4dec401fc3e5182f49f8e22ca4bc59","tid":1552748,"uid":318070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:52:29.000